### Submit a new job (Alpine test)
POST http://localhost:5213/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "alpine-sleep-test",
  "containerImage": "alpine:3.22.1",
  "command": ["sh"],
  "args": ["-c", "echo 'Starting Alpine container job...' && sleep 30 && echo 'Job completed!'"],
  "configuration": {
    "LOG_LEVEL": "INFO",
    "JOB_TYPE": "test"
  },
  "labels": {
    "app": "test-job",
    "environment": "dev"
  }
}

### Get all jobs (with Kubernetes info)
GET http://localhost:5213/api/jobs

### Get jobs by status
GET http://localhost:5213/api/jobs?status=Queued

### Get specific job (replace with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:5213/api/jobs/{{jobId}}

### Refresh Kubernetes info for a specific job
POST http://localhost:5213/api/jobs/{{jobId}}/refresh-kubernetes-info

### Cancel a job (replace with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5213/api/jobs/{{jobId}}

### === KUBERNETES RESOURCES ENDPOINTS ===

### Get all Kubernetes jobs
GET http://localhost:5213/api/kubernetes/jobs

### Get specific Kubernetes job
GET http://localhost:5213/api/kubernetes/jobs/{{kubernetesJobName}}

### Get pods for a specific Kubernetes job
GET http://localhost:5213/api/kubernetes/jobs/{{kubernetesJobName}}/pods

### Get complete resource info for a job (job + pods)
GET http://localhost:5213/api/kubernetes/jobs/{{kubernetesJobName}}/resource-info

### Get all pods
GET http://localhost:5213/api/kubernetes/pods

### Get specific pod
GET http://localhost:5213/api/kubernetes/pods/{{podName}}

### Get pod logs
GET http://localhost:5213/api/kubernetes/pods/{{podName}}/logs

### Get pod logs from specific container
GET http://localhost:5213/api/kubernetes/pods/{{podName}}/logs?containerName={{containerName}}

### Delete Kubernetes job
DELETE http://localhost:5213/api/kubernetes/jobs/{{kubernetesJobName}}

